name: ℭ𝔥𝔞𝔬𝔰 𝔦𝔫 ℑ 𝔞𝔫𝔡 ℌ𝔢𝔯 [𝔭𝔞𝔯𝔱 𝔱𝔴𝔬]
description: "Day to day, day by day, the chaos still resides. All the facades that I have putted up until now, still lurks the truth. I do not know when it will show its fangs and hunt me down.  As of now, hide me from the chaos in the shadow, until the day finally come, when it decides to seek vengeance."
